We don't support ubutun 17 quite yet. What version of gcc are you using?

I think it's likely to have been an out of memory error. Please check dmesg to verify. It should say that cc1plus has been sacrificed.

body:
We don't support ubutun 17 quite yet. What version of gcc are you using?

I think it's likely to have been an out of memory error. Please check `dmesg` to verify. It should say that `cc1plus` has been sacrificed.
